Gateway Load Balancer

Deploy, scale and manage a fleet of 3rd party network virtual appliances in AWS

Example: Firewalls, Intrusion Detection and Prevention Systems, Deep packety inspection systems, Payload Manipulations.....

Basically a secondary security load balancer
From user->glb->target group->glb->Application

Operates at Layer 3 Network layer for IP packets
Combines the following functions
  Transparent Network Gateway - single entry/exit for all traffic
  Load balancer - distributes traffic to your virtual machines
Uses the GENEVE protocol on port 6081

Target groups
  EC2 instances
  Private IP addresses
